&lt;h1 id="why-you-cant-hire"&gt;Why You Can&amp;rsquo;t Hire&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dec 13 2011&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There isn&amp;rsquo;t a shortage of developers and designers. There&amp;rsquo;s a surplus of founders.&lt;/p&gt;
